./forward.py [$host [$port]]
tcpdump -l ... | ./tcpdumped.sh $event | ./forward.py
ngrep -lt -W single ... | ./ngrepped.sh [$event] | ./forward.py

In general, you must avoid buffering stdout and stdin for everything in the
pipe. Examples:

    tcpdump -l
    ngrep -l
    gsed -u
    grep --line-buffered
    awk '{...; fflush()}'

The scripts and forward.py don't need a special argument.

Read the scripts for more details/usage.
